tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE emergency_vehicles (
  vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  vehicle_type VARCHAR(255),
  location VARCHAR(255),
  availability BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE vehicle_logs (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  vehicle_id INT,
  log_time TIMESTAMP,
  event_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE users (
  user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  username VARCHAR(255),
  password VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE dispatch_logs (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  vehicle_id INT,
  station_id INT,
  dispatch_time TIMESTAMP,
  return_time TIMESTAMP,
  FOREIGN KEY (vehicle_id) REFERENCES emergency_response_vehicles(vehicle_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (station_id) REFERENCES emergency_stations(station_id)
);

CREATE TABLE emergency_vehicles (
    vehicle_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    location VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    available BOOLEAN NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE vehicle_maintenance (
    maintenance_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id UUID REFERENCES emergency_vehicles(vehicle_id),
    maintenance_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    maintenance_date DATE NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE vehicle_tracking (
    tracking_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id UUID REFERENCES emergency_vehicles(vehicle_id),
    latitude DOUBLE PRECISION NOT NULL,
    longitude DOUBLE PRECISION NOT NULL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE vehicle_assignments (
    assignment_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id UUID REFERENCES emergency_vehicles(vehicle_id),
    dispatch_id UUID,
    assignment_date DATE NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE vehicle_availability (
  availability_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  vehicle_id UUID,
  availability_status VARCHAR(50),
  available_from TIMESTAMP,
  available_until TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE vehicle_maintenance (
  maintenance_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  vehicle_id UUID,
  maintenance_type VARCHAR(50),
  maintenance_details TEXT,
  maintenance_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE vehicle_dispatch (
  dispatch_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  vehicle_id UUID,
  dispatch_type VARCHAR(50),
  dispatch_location TEXT,
  dispatch_time TIMESTAMP
);
